OL,5, A watchdog's intervention into the     
OL,6, Captain Tom Foundation had a "massive  
OL,7, adverse impact" on fundraising, the    
OL,8, charity's latest accounts show.        
OL,10,FIt was set up by the family of the NHS 
OL,11,Ffundraiser soon after he died in 2021. 
OL,13,FIncome had been over #1m for the 2021  
OL,14,Ffinancial year, but fell to #402,854   
OL,15,Ffrom June 2021 to November 2022.       
OL,17,FThe Charity Commission launched an     
OL,18,Finquiry last year after identifying    
OL,19,Fconcerns about the charity's management
OL,20,Fand independence from Sir Tom's family.
